---
title: Lemon Aioli Crab Cakes with Fingerling Potatoes and an Arugula and Tomato Salad
description: Crab is one of the gems of the sea: it’s tender and sweet in ways that other shellfish can only aspire to. So when our chefs devised this recipe with ready-to-cook crab cakes, we knew it would be impossible to resist. The cakes have just enough breading and veggies to give them the perfect amount of moistness, tenderness, and crunch. To let them really shine, we’re keeping the sides simple: a salad with lemon dressing and potatoes roasted with smoked paprika.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/crab-cakes-under-a-meyer-lemon-dressed-salad-a69e66d3.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/crab-cakes-under-a-meyer-lemon-dressed-salad-5d35cc28e203d200173c36a8-9bb21348.pdf
course: main course
servings: 2
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/crab-cakes-under-a-meyer-lemon-dressed-salad-5d35cc28e203d200173c36a8
author: HelloFresh
time required: 35 minutes
nutrition:
  calories: 860 kcal
  fat: 61 g
  saturated fat: 14 g
